<span id="freeTextContainer14150327554134068246">UM WHAT.<br/><br/>THIS WAS SO GOOD. How did I wait so long to read it? <br/><br/>I&apos;ll post a full review at some point - but there&apos;s so many good ones out there already. For now, I&apos;ll just say that I don&apos;t normally like futuristic dystopians all that much (Marie Lu aside because she&apos;s an absolute queen) but omg I loved this one. <br/><br/>The hubs and I actually read it together on audio, and we laughed are way through it -and where shocked out of our chairs more than once.<br/><br/>Well done, Mr. Shusterman. Well done.</span>
  <span id="freeText14150327554134068246" style="display:none">UM WHAT.<br /><br />THIS WAS SO GOOD. How did I wait so long to read it? <br /><br />I'll post a full review at some point - but there's so many good ones out there already. For now, I'll just say that I don't normally like futuristic dystopians all that much (Marie Lu aside because she's an absolute queen) but omg I loved this one. <br /><br />The hubs and I actually read it together on audio, and we laughed are way through it -and where shocked out of our chairs more than once.<br /><br />Well done, Mr. Shusterman. Well done.</span>
